pageContext.claim: “You know, when this came out, it was "quid pro quo." Well, there was none.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump insists that there was "no quid pro quo" in his call with Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky but texts released of U.S. diplomats working under him indicate that they thought the president was linking the release of promised military aid to whether the new government pursued investigations of the Biden family and the Democratic National Committee.
